[As in all the other states reporting cases of A(H3N2)v influenza virus infection, illness has been mild and there has been no record of onward human-to-human transmission of infection. It is likely that human cases of A (H3N2)v influenza virus infection will be reported from most, if not all, states hosting agricultural fairs.

The interactive HealthMap of Pennsylvania can be accessed at http://healthmap.org/r/37gn. - Mod.CP]
